title: The November Man

subTitle: Cade Yeager, a struggling single father discovers a damaged truck which turns out to be Optimus Prime. Together with the remaining Autobots, he and his family must rise to face an impending threat.

title: Mission: Impossible II
subTitle: Agent Ethan Hunt fights against a rogue terrorist and rushes to prevent a deadly virus from spreading. To avert a global catastrophe, Ethan has to bring everything to an end.

subTitle: The Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles are bigger and better than ever in this blockbuster hit loaded with nonstop action and laughs! When New York City is in trouble, it's up to these four ninja-fighting, pizza-loving brothers to save it.

title: Tomb Raider
subTitle: Lara Croft undertakes a dangerous journey by travelling to the last known location of her missing father, to unravel the truth behind his mysterious disappearance.
